/>\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"98a8cc1d3eaa9c80b46c60ecd413dc76381e7634","tid":1777323,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:17:10.000Z","msg":"icac係特首旗下架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf6ad067ee05c9fa07c3010bf3e076ef56d10a5","tid":1777323,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42a55dd3c3761812de5cd70ff4c1c96d153ff618","tid":1777323,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"ICAC 係做咩嫁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:17:21.000Z","msg":"包庇689"},{"pid":"ebdfca95a0c556be563ac09812437b8b3c8d47e3","tid":1777323,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cf6ad067ee05c9fa07c3010bf3e076ef56d10a5","tid":1777323,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42a55dd3c3761812de5cd70ff4c1c96d153ff618","tid":1777323,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"ICAC 係做咩嫁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:17:21.000Z","msg":"包庇689"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:19:01.000Z","msg":"689: 香港勝在有icac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a65e5f9e9f71fd123ae6c161582825edbae37f3","tid":1777323,"uid":119271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42a55dd3c3761812de5cd70ff4c1c96d153ff618","tid":1777323,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"ICAC 係做咩嫁？"},"citedBy":0,"rep